Rating: 3
I don't think I would have liked these as much had I used low-fat or fat-free cream cheese. They were tasty with regular cream cheese, though I only could eat about 3. I too would recommend serving them with a dessert plate or as one of a few light appetizers in the summer.

Rating: 4
I could not move around the room fast enough with these grapes! My guests went crazy for them and I have had to pass on the recipe numerous times.

Rating: 1
